this.isLoadingTable = false; - repeating code. I wish if it could look like try{} catch{} function in c#. Is it possible?

```
this.visitorService.getAllCurrentVisitorsList(this.query).subscribe( (data) => {
      this.visitors = data;
    }, error => {
    },
    {
      this.isLoadingTable = false;
     }
);
```

Thank you for attention!

